### Fetch indicators – invalid block (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/fetch-indicators?block=invalid

### Fetch indicators – rates (default 90-day range)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/fetch-indicators?block=rates

### Fetch indicators – rates with explicit range
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/fetch-indicators?block=rates&start=2026-01-01&end=2026-01-05
